{"word":"H6728 - צִיִּי - tsîyîy - tsee-ee' - Wild beast of the desert","slug":"H6728","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">צִיִּי</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>tsîyîy"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>tsee-ee'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Wild beast of the desert"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E6;&#x05D9;&#x05BC;&#x05D9; - ts&#x0131;&#x0302;y&#x0131;&#x0302;y</b> - <i>tsee-ee'</i><p/>From the same as <a href=\"#/H6723\">H6723</a>; a <i>desert dweller</i>, that is, <i>nomad</i> or wild <i>beast: - </i>wild beast of the desert, that dwell in (inhabiting) the wilderness."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3328\">H3328</a>, <a href=\"#/H6713\">H6713</a>, <a href=\"#/H6714\">H6714</a>, <a href=\"#/H6715\">H6715</a>, <a href=\"#/H6716\">H6716</a>, <a href=\"#/H6717\">H6717</a>, <a href=\"#/H6721\">H6721</a>, <a href=\"#/H6722\">H6722</a>"}]}